source: TEXT_CMNDEFCHOCOBORENAME_00134_MY_CHOCOBO_RENAME_UNQUALIFIED<tab>You cannot perform this action while your companion is present.
TEXT_CMNDEFCHOCOBORENAME_00134_PROMPT_MY_CHOCOBO_RENAME_MES0<tab>Names must be between 2 and 20 alphabetic characters and can include apostrophes but not hyphens.
TEXT_CMNDEFCHOCOBORENAME_00134_MY_CHOCOBO_RENAME_STABLE<tab>You cannot perform this action while your chocobo is stabled.
